Text: Jūgendstila metāla kalumi un jumta apjoms atgādina kādu Budapeštas gastro tirgu. Skaists potenciāls ir Vidzemes tirgus gaļas paviljonā. https://t.co/QF5aqh3bup
English: Art Nouveau metal forgings and the size of the roof are reminiscent of a Budapest gastro market. The meat pavilion of Vidzeme Market has beautiful potential. https://t.co/QF5aqh3bup

Text: Ķekavā pie TC Liiba jauns gruzīnu virtuves food truck “Gamarjoba”. Viss, ko paņēmu garšīgs un svaigs, ļoti laipna īpašniece, iesaku pamēģināt, ja gribas jaunas garšas! https://t.co/BPdXNeZqze
English: In the bunch at TC Liiba, a new Georgian food truck “Gamarjoba”. Everything I picked up tasty and fresh, a very kind owner, I recommend giving it a try if you want new flavors! https://t.co/BPdXNeZqze

Text: Mēģināju Čiepai izskaidrot, ka es arī esmu cilvēks un gribu paēst vakariņas, bet viņai tas nebija svarīgi un uz būri atteicās iet... Tā nu es gaidu kad varēs krāsni darbināt kad saimniece izlems iet gulēt. https://t.co/azbFQS38It
English: I tried to explain to Chip that I was human too and wanted to eat dinner, but she didn't care and refused to go to the cage... So I'm waiting to operate the oven when the host decides to go to bed. https://t.co/azbFQS38It
